thread.title: Sharon, Passport Dinners
thread.title_full: Rubber Stamp Champ reviewed by Sharon, Passport Dinners

author: Sharon, Passport Dinners
title: Sharon, Passport Dinners
text: I use different stamps for each of my theme dinner boxes. Rubber Stamp Champ has come through each time. Except I did have an issue with my last one, but I fault my design. I contacted them, and they quickly helped me design a better stamp, and it was quickly delivered. Thanks!
